34  OptimalFanEfficiency(FanType const fanType, const double fanSpeed, const double flowRate, const double inletPressure,
35  const double outletPressure, const double compressibility)

37  inletPressure(inletPressure), compressibility(compressibility)

44  double calculate() {
45  FanTypeProperties const & currentFan = fanTypeProperties[static_cast<std::size_t>(fanType)];
46  double specificSpeed = (fanSpeed * std::sqrt(flowRate)) / (std::pow(outletPressure - inletPressure, 0.75)
47  * std::pow(compressibility, 0.25));
48 
49  if (specificSpeed < currentFan.minSpecificSpeed) {
50  specificSpeed = currentFan.minSpecificSpeed;
51  } else if (specificSpeed > currentFan.maxSpecificSpeed) {
52  specificSpeed = currentFan.maxSpecificSpeed;
53  }
54 
55  bool isPolynomial = specificSpeed < currentFan.transition;
56  if (isPolynomial) {
57  return currentFan.polynomialFunction(specificSpeed);
58  }
59  return currentFan.exponentialFunction(specificSpeed);
60  }
61 
62 private:
63  FanType const fanType;
64  const double fanSpeed, flowRate, outletPressure, inletPressure, compressibility;
65

67  struct FanTypeProperties {
68  private:
76  FanTypeProperties(const FanType fanType, const double transition, const double minSpecificSpeed, const double maxSpecificSpeed,
77  std::function<double (double n)> polynomialFunction,
78  std::function<double (double n)> exponentialFunction = [](double n) { return 0; })
79  : fanType(fanType), transition(transition), minSpecificSpeed(minSpecificSpeed), maxSpecificSpeed(maxSpecificSpeed),
80  polynomialFunction(std::move(polynomialFunction)), exponentialFunction(std::move(exponentialFunction))
81  {}
82 
83  const FanType fanType;
84  const double transition, minSpecificSpeed, maxSpecificSpeed;
85  const std::function<double (double n)> polynomialFunction;
86  const std::function<double (double n)> exponentialFunction;
87  friend class OptimalFanEfficiency;
88  };
